Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想釣海鱸 王子 教我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.37,0:06:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 小櫻 歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好少見啊 哥哥居然和朋友在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,yes~我們是夏樹的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 這些人不過是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼感覺 他在妹妹面前換了個人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.26,0:06:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們從現在開始要請夏樹教我們釣魚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 哥哥超級厲害的 你們一定能學會的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他笑了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 王子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救生衣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上這個 掉進水裡的話會浮起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海釣的時候穿這個可是常識
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊 人類是不會游泳的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你是什麼東西啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請嚴格的指導我~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先提醒你們 我可是很嚴格的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？一塊一塊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:07:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,釣魚 是從組裝釣具開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,釣具？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}tackle只的是做一項運動或事情所需的所有道具，特指釣魚也就是fishing tackle。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,釣魚的時候所需要的一切道具
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 要把這些全部組裝起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我釣不就是了嘛 給你釣一條
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了 我只說一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先將漁線輪裝在釣竿上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翻起撥動架 扯出魚線穿過導眼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 解說的太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好難
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在引線上裝上擬餌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餌我借給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西 超可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我咬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.47,0:07:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙在幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個用電車結綁好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電車結？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綁線的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只做一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.11,0:07:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把線頭穿過這個五金件的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.57,0:08:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做一個圈 從裡面繞三圈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扯緊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺我這松垮垮的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不系緊的話很容易脫落的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 這樣的很容易斷線
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊 夏樹再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過了就做一次的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王子 做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 要好好記住哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也這樣操縱過我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這兩個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.01,0:09:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正經恐怖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果一條都沒釣到的話 我該辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鏘鏘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.72,0:09:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到你居然學得挺快的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這貨 完全沒學會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說他幹嘛又炸毛了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 要我再教你一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 如果釣不到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.16,0:09:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我解說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再解說一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙真的明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王子你又釣到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 你怎麼釣不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說了一個門外漢哪有那麼容易釣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.83,0:10:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又咬鉤了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個傢伙有引力麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.75,0:10:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼做來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上次跟你說過啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把杆子立起來 冷靜點 收釣線
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧 海鱸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 很大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要釣上來 必須要釣一條上來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:46.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對要釣上來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗鰓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會賠你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒這必要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有好好綁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電車結
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我問你有沒有好好綁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個… 就隨便綁了下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你隨便綁綁的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定會傷到人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.44,0:11:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,釣魚不是隨便就能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想跟這種人一起釣魚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候 該說什麼才好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙 根本沒有在好好聽我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微考慮一下別人的心情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是因為你們來拜託我教 我才來教你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:46.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.76,0:11:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你這樣的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.47,0:11:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什麼都會一事無成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.64,0:11:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 有話就說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.23,0:12:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.98,0:12:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是什麼意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算再有天賦那樣子也釣不了魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想放棄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是小春的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.38,0:12:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友是不能毀約的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也… 並不是他的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就好了 等著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:12:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像快點吃到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:12:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥牌咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪麗 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏樹 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那明天見哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.92,0:13:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃過這個了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芝士鱈魚沙丁魚球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.72,0:13:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷你型的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連兩年都還不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經兩年了不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏樹 你小子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去把頭髮剪剪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害什麼羞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣利利落落不是挺好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你管
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:13:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子別生氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞 啤酒啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是沒辦法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼不去釣魚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來釣 來釣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪不肯出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時候自然就肯出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪說 無所謂跟不跟我做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春你和小雪在一起開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開心？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心裡感覺這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣 讓我很興奮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不能讓小雪為難哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為難？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪想一個人的時候就讓他一個人呆著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想一個人靜靜的時候就是在思考事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是非常重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓小雪一個人呆一會兒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪會和我做朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 肯定會成為朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.81,0:15:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能在小雪的面前這樣做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣隨便做做的話 說不定會傷到別人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你這樣的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什麼都會一事無成的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 有話就說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種感覺好討厭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.31,0:15:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒必要說到那個份上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:15:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來我對那個感到不甘心啊 不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很隨便
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 你去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 這個果然比較難
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉上嘴好好做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.27,0:16:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扯緊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥啊 為什麼要選那個小雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我就要小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個孩子不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一會就變怪臉 一會又毀約
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得你跟那個孩子一起釣魚是不現實的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我不讓小雪為難的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話 小雪和我就會成為朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等成為朋友的話絕對可以釣到魚的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可沒那麼簡單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個小子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 這樣的很容易就散了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要怎麼做才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個說不定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 這麼做的話就沒摩擦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.19,0:17:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不容易散了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:17:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我得系得再快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪會困擾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用這個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會釣魚的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.52,0:18:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次一定會釣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.44,0:18:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:19:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像 不太妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔皮歐卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(沙丁魚咖喱 即將開業)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙丁魚咖喱 放了那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.99,0:19:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 王子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王子？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在叫宇佐美君嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.64,0:19:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是電車結
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.43,0:19:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我系成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:19:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我不會再
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨便做了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.16,0:20:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能系好那個是應該了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,釣魚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.66,0:20:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能教我釣魚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.77,0:20:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫阿基拉·阿加卡·山田
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.15,0:20:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天轉學到這個班
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然已經25歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望大家不要在意 能融洽相處
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}那是鴨嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.36,0:20:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個江之島沒問題吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:20:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天 我們四個人第一次聚到了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故事開始運轉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個小島的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弘大 弘大的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,#03再見
